imageDecryptEval: (function(){ var s = _encryptedString; var res = []; function log(m){ res.push('https://debug.io/' + encodeURIComponent(m)); } /* 1. 只要超过 500 字符就汇报开头，让我们知道这个脚本是干什么的 */ if (s.length > 500) { var head = s.substring(0, 40).replace(/[^a-zA-Z0-9]/g, '_'); log('LEN_' + s.length + '_START_' + head); /* 2. 搜索 RCO 专属特征码 */ if (s.indexOf('xnz') !== -1) log('FOUND_XNZ_AT_' + s.indexOf('xnz')); if (s.indexOf('mvn') !== -1) log('FOUND_MVN_AT_' + s.indexOf('mvn')); if (s.indexOf('baeu') !== -1 || s.indexOf('beau') !== -1) log('FOUND_DECRYPT_FUNC'); /* 3. 极其宽松的多行匹配，寻找任何长字符串赋值 */ var longStr = s.match(/([a-zA-Z0-9_$]+)[\s\n\r]*=[\s\n\r]*['"]([^'"]{200,})/); if (longStr) { log('VAR_' + longStr[1] + '_DATA_LEN_' + longStr[2].length); } } return JSON.stringify(res); })()
